text: Labo National High School (Labo NHS or LNHS) is a secondary school located at Brgy. Labo, Ozamiz, Philippines. Labo has only 2 educational institution along with Labo Central School. Most of the students are coming from its barangay and nearby like Cabunga-an, Embargo, Molicay, Kinangay, Gata, Gutokan, Sangay, Capucao, Carangan, and Bacolod Mentering. ==External links== * Official Facebook Page Category:Education in Ozamiz Category:Schools in Misamis Occidental Category:High schools in the Philippines
